236
00:46:08,574 --> 00:46:10,793
so they went in a roundabout way.

237
00:46:11,254 --> 00:46:15,720
So God said alright, go ahead, find out for yourself and then He’ll

238
00:46:22,505 --> 00:46:27,269
come and give at the last when you will be ready to receive the Truth.

239
00:46:44,824 --> 00:46:49,090
And even now I am telling you can get it without any difficulty,

240
00:47:08,875 --> 00:47:12,155
it’s your own right, you have it, it’s your own,

241
00:47:12,235 --> 00:47:15,901
still people are finding it difficult in their freedom.

242
00:47:15,981 --> 00:47:18,127
So that is human being you see.

243
00:47:37,812 --> 00:47:39,478
He can’t accept anything.

244
00:47:39,558 --> 00:47:42,358
They have to learn though making mistakes,

245
00:47:42,438 --> 00:47:45,104
going into problems, then they learn it.

246
00:47:45,184 --> 00:47:50,547
Sometimes they are too conditioned, sometimes they are too egoistical

247
00:48:27,063 --> 00:48:30,996
and they cannot discriminate between the Truth and untruth.

248
00:48:45,322 --> 00:48:49,522
Q: Right now Colombia is going through a very difficult period,

249
00:48:49,602 --> 00:48:51,135
with a lot of violence.

250
00:48:52,110 --> 00:48:56,243
Do you have any explanation of why this is happening here now,

251
00:48:56,323 --> 00:48:59,789
and what is the method through which we can help it?

252
00:49:00,880 --> 00:49:07,082
There are many things to be seen to that have created problems

253
00:49:07,162 --> 00:49:11,028
of violence everywhere in the world – it is not only here.

254
00:49:12,012 --> 00:49:15,545
But the problem comes from our wrong, man-made ideas.

255
00:49:33,377 --> 00:49:37,650
For example, take democracy or communism – we have tried both.

256
00:49:37,730 --> 00:49:42,463
In democracy, what we do is to allow an individual to have his own way:

257
00:49:42,543 --> 00:49:47,009
let the individual grow, and we don't worry about the collectivity.

258
00:49:47,089 --> 00:49:49,422
So the individual becomes important

259
00:49:49,502 --> 00:49:51,635
and starts growing in a big way,

260
00:49:51,715 --> 00:49:57,181
and he can become a madman who suppresses others, not caring about the collective.

261
00:49:57,261 --> 00:50:02,261
And democracy is money-oriented: some make money and become greedy – money,

262
00:50:02,341 --> 00:50:07,141
money, money, like mad – so you become rich, but you also become wilder.

263
00:50:07,221 --> 00:50:11,154
In the communist ideology they worry about the collectivity

264
00:50:11,234 --> 00:50:14,367
and not about the individual, so the individual

265
00:50:14,447 --> 00:50:16,716
becomes absolutely weak and helpless;

266
00:50:16,796 --> 00:50:21,196
and what is the use of doing things collectively with weak people?

267
00:50:21,276 --> 00:50:22,942
So both ways have failed.

268
00:50:23,022 --> 00:50:25,888
A very powerful politician from London came

269
00:50:25,968 --> 00:50:28,901
and told Me that she is fed up with the left

270
00:50:28,981 --> 00:50:31,914
and the right and wants to be in the centre,

271
00:50:31,994 --> 00:50:34,727
so she is starting a party in the centre.

272
00:50:34,807 --> 00:50:36,407
I said, what is the use?

273
00:50:36,487 --> 00:50:39,926
If you are in the centre, you will have no movement.

274
00:50:40,006 --> 00:50:42,272
These are all man-made ideologies.

275
00:50:42,352 --> 00:50:46,165
If you are in the centre, you should be ascent-oriented;

276
00:50:53,078 --> 00:50:56,158
then you become a very different personality.

277
00:51:03,258 --> 00:51:08,471
I would say: supposing I have all the powers, I am a capitalist – but I am

278
00:51:14,161 --> 00:51:18,894
also a communist, because I cannot enjoy it by Myself, I must share it.

279
00:51:23,200 --> 00:51:28,181
So all these man-made theories get integrated in Sahaja Yoga,

280
00:51:28,261 --> 00:51:32,476
and you start really enjoying the truth after Sahaja Yoga.

281
00:51:44,241 --> 00:51:51,040
In Sahaja Yoga the individual is nourished, is balanced and enjoys his joy,

282
00:51:51,120 --> 00:51:56,186
and the whole collectivity is within him – he can feel the whole collective.

283
00:52:02,400 --> 00:52:05,933
And we do not live with theories, but with the truth.

284
00:52:15,102 --> 00:52:19,435
You can feel the truth: supposing you want to know, is there God?

285
00:52:20,202 --> 00:52:23,202
Just put out your hands and ask the question,

286
00:52:23,320 --> 00:52:29,597
and you start getting the tremendous, nice vibrations, filled with joy.

287
00:52:31,320 --> 00:52:35,253
Now, let Me ask the majority – what does the majority want,

288
00:53:15,718 --> 00:53:19,851
realization or questions? [The audience asks for realization.]

289
00:53:19,931 --> 00:53:22,131
So, better have your realization.

290
00:53:28,047 --> 00:53:33,580
You can write down your questions and I will try to answer them; it is not endless.

291
00:53:33,660 --> 00:53:39,684
Again I give you the message: if the food is ready, it is better to eat it.

292
00:54:03,100 --> 00:54:08,500
I wish all of you could sit down, because you don't have to see anything anymore.

293
00:54:17,921 --> 00:54:22,054
And those who do not want to have their realization should go,

294
00:54:23,183 --> 00:54:27,141
because it will disturb

295
00:54:27,221 --> 00:54:29,687
others; if you have no desire for it,

296
00:54:29,767 --> 00:54:33,500
it is better that you leave the hall, without any anger.

297
00:54:33,580 --> 00:54:38,913
I was very happy to learn that in this country Mother Earth is highly respected.

298
00:55:00,301 --> 00:55:04,816
The chakra which controls the innocence – and also the abode

299
00:55:06,881 --> 00:55:10,909
of the Kundalini – is made of

300
00:55:10,989 --> 00:55:15,017
the element of Mother Earth.

301
00:55:16,461 --> 00:55:21,406
Now I would request you all to take off your shoes and put your feet

302
00:55:35,695 --> 00:55:40,161
on Mother Earth, if possible, so that she takes away your problems.

303
00:55:40,241 --> 00:55:44,479
Those who are sitting on the ground need not,

304
00:56:02,461 --> 00:56:06,194
but take off the shoes; it also increases the attention.

305
00:56:07,521 --> 00:56:12,987
Everybody can sit down – there is nothing to be seen – you can sit in the passage,

306
00:56:19,222 --> 00:56:24,100
it is all right.

307
00:56:24,840 --> 00:56:27,506
I did not expect so many people to come.

308
00:56:38,222 --> 00:56:44,219
Now I have to tell you that in our procedure we put the left hand towards Me,

309
00:57:05,301 --> 00:57:10,236
very comfortably,

310
00:57:10,316 --> 00:57:13,496
like this.

311
00:57:15,942 --> 00:57:21,075
The left hand is the power of your desire, symbolic of your desire to achieve

312
00:57:27,720 --> 00:57:33,050
your realization; keep it comfortable,

313
00:57:33,130 --> 00:57:36,470
with the fingers pointing towards Me.

314
00:57:45,061 --> 00:57:52,726
The right hand is used for the power of action, to release your chakras,

315
00:58:39,342 --> 00:58:46,480
and it will also teach you how

316
00:58:46,560 --> 00:58:48,520
to raise your own Kundalini.

317
00:58:49,243 --> 00:58:54,443
The first and foremost thing is that we have to enter into the Kingdom of God,

318
00:58:57,500 --> 00:59:02,839
and you are at the epitome of your evolution now.

319
00:59:09,924 --> 00:59:14,390
That is why you should not feel guilty at all; you should be happy.

320
00:59:18,501 --> 00:59:23,492
After all, human beings can only make mistakes – we are not God.

321
00:59:27,142 --> 00:59:31,960
So forget the past, just forget the past, and be here in the present.

322
00:59:46,241 --> 00:59:50,610
Do not count your mistakes,

323
00:59:54,868 --> 01:00:00,468
do not count your miseries – just be happy with yourself and have love for yourself.

324
01:00:00,548 --> 01:00:07,614
This is the basic condition: only happy people can enter the Kingdom of God.

325
01:00:14,741 --> 01:00:20,914
So forgive yourself, forgive yourself.

326
01:00:30,305 --> 01:00:34,371
Now please close your eyes; you can take off your spectacles,

327
01:00:36,041 --> 01:00:39,646
because you don't have to see anything.

328
01:00:50,400 --> 01:00:54,666
Put your left hand towards Me and your right hand on your heart,

329
01:01:03,360 --> 01:01:05,057
and close your eyes.

330
01:01:06,544 --> 01:01:09,544
Here you have to ask Me a question – “Mother,

331
01:01:11,080 --> 01:01:16,258
am I the Spirit?” – ask it three times; it is a very fundamental question.

332
01:01:16,338 --> 01:01:18,138
Watch yourself, not others;

333
01:01:18,218 --> 01:01:22,951
this is the only time you have to see yourself, so keep your eyes shut.

334
01:01:23,031 --> 01:01:26,164
This question means that if you are the Spirit,

335
01:01:26,244 --> 01:01:29,044
you become your own master, your own guru.

336
01:01:29,124 --> 01:01:32,990
Now put your right hand on the upper part of your abdomen,

337
01:01:33,070 --> 01:01:36,803
on the left-hand side, and ask Me another question three

338
01:01:36,883 --> 01:01:41,242
times: “Mother, am I my own master?” Now take your right hand

339
01:01:41,322 --> 01:01:45,122
to the lower part of your abdomen, on the left-hand side.

340
01:10:01,441 --> 01:10:08,937
Here I cannot take away your freedom; in your freedom you have to say six times,

341
01:10:11,950 --> 01:10:17,393
“Mother, please give me the pure knowledge,” because this centre has six petals.

342
01:10:31,421 --> 01:10:38,123
As you ask, the Kundalini starts moving upward; make way for the Kundalini.

343
01:11:47,561 --> 01:11:54,160
Now take your hand to the upper part of your abdomen,

344
01:11:54,682 --> 01:11:59,890
on the left-hand side, and say with full confidence ten times,

345
01:12:08,520 --> 01:12:13,622
“Mother, I am my own master.” Now raise your hand to your

346
01:12:56,061 --> 01:13:03,089
heart and say with full confidence twelve times, “Mother, I am

347
01:13:13,401 --> 01:13:19,947
the Spirit.” We have to know that the Divine is the ocean of love,

348
01:13:35,703 --> 01:13:41,281
grace and bliss, but above all it is the ocean of

349
01:13:41,361 --> 01:13:46,907
forgiveness – so we have to forgive ourselves;

350
01:13:58,801 --> 01:14:05,659
for what mistake can we commit that this ocean of love cannot forgive?

351
01:14:21,203 --> 01:14:26,753
Now raise your right hand to the corner of your neck and shoulder,

352
01:14:48,941 --> 01:14:53,474
turning your head to the right, and say with full confidence sixteen

353
01:15:10,421 --> 01:15:17,150
times, “Mother, I am not guilty at all”; and if you still feel guilty,

354
01:15:26,300 --> 01:15:30,366
say it a hundred and eight times, because you are not guilty.

355
01:16:00,941 --> 01:16:06,518
Now put your hand across your forehead and press it on both sides;

356
01:16:16,900 --> 01:16:19,166
this is the centre of forgiveness.

357
01:16:23,220 --> 01:16:28,207
Say, “Mother, I forgive everyone.” You may say it is difficult,

358
01:16:38,042 --> 01:16:40,042
but it is a myth – whether you

359
01:16:40,122 --> 01:16:43,300
forgive or not; and if you do not forgive,

360
01:16:44,241 --> 01:16:47,841
you play into wrong hands, so it is better to forgive.

361
01:17:06,947 --> 01:17:08,480
Say it from your heart.

362
01:17:14,562 --> 01:17:19,179
Now take your hand to the back of your head and rest your head on it;

363
01:17:22,742 --> 01:17:25,041
for your own satisfaction,

364
01:17:25,121 --> 01:17:30,987
without feeling guilty and without counting your mistakes,

365
01:17:44,420 --> 01:17:47,520
say, “O God, please forgive me for

366
01:17:47,600 --> 01:17:52,333
whatever I have done wrong.” Now stretch your hand on top of your head,

367
01:18:06,561 --> 01:18:08,361
over the fontanel bone area

368
01:18:08,441 --> 01:18:11,880
– this is very important – stretch your fingers,

369
01:18:23,944 --> 01:18:27,262
press it down, and move your scalp seven times.

370
01:18:27,342 --> 01:18:31,614
As I cannot force you, ask Me in your own freedom: “Mother,

371
01:18:34,182 --> 01:18:40,358
please give me my Realization.” Move your scalp seven times and ask seven times.

372
01:19:52,622 --> 01:19:56,488
Now please take down your hands and slowly open your eyes.

373
01:20:03,745 --> 01:20:05,478
Watch Me without thinking.

374
01:20:09,721 --> 01:20:15,216
Stretch your right hand towards Me and put your left hand on top of your head,

375
01:20:22,376 --> 01:20:23,909
bend your head, and see

376
01:20:23,989 --> 01:20:28,522
for yourself whether there is a cool breeze coming out of your head;

377
01:20:28,602 --> 01:20:31,105
some people get it close, some far.

378
01:20:43,421 --> 01:20:46,549
Now change hands and feel with the right hand.

379
01:21:41,481 --> 01:21:44,747
Push back your head and ask three times: “Mother,

380
01:21:47,564 --> 01:21:50,548
is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?

381
01:21:50,628 --> 01:21:52,094
Is this the Chaitanya?

382
01:21:52,880 --> 01:21:58,644
Is this the all-pervading power of God's love?” – ask any one of these, three times.

383
01:22:25,281 --> 01:22:29,188
Now put down your hands and feel the breeze.

384
01:22:41,660 --> 01:22:47,360
Those who have felt it, on the fontanel bone area and on their hands,

385
01:22:48,226 --> 01:22:49,840
please raise both hands.

386
01:23:07,264 --> 01:23:10,197
I bow to all of you – you are divine people.

387
01:23:16,901 --> 01:23:22,030
Now you have got it; so beautiful it is.

388
01:23:32,621 --> 01:23:37,154
I don't know how I will leave Bogota tomorrow, leaving you all here.

